title: About + FAQ
text:
Hi! Welcome to my little website. On this site, you will find selected writings and other works that I am proud of.

Frequently asked questions:

What are your cats named?
– Juice and Onion
Where did you get your glasses?
– Warby Parker! Although, I am currently shopping around for a more premium pair.
What’s your favorite month?
– I love November. I am a big fan of when it’s chilly enough outside to justify wearing a nice coat, but not cold to the point that I look like the Michelin man!
Where are you from?
– I was born in Florida and moved to Georgia when I was 10. I’ve spent most of my life in the Southeast, but during the pandemic I picked up and moved to Maine for the heck of it!

title: Welcome to the homepage!
text:
My name is Jessica and I made this website to display works I’ve produced that I’m proud of!
Use the navigation bar to find my selected writing samples and a little FAQ page.
I’m glad you’re here. Thanks for stopping by!

I certify that the work included in this portfolio is my own original work. Work included which was conducted as a part of a team or other group is indicated and attributed as such - the other team members are named and a true description of my role in the project is included.
